Take 1 mL of freshly prepared HAIR/CTF NPs and transfer it to a 10 kDa ultrafiltration centrifuge tube. Centrifuge at 5000 g for 15 min to remove unencapsulated free drugs. Calculate the drug concentration in the filtrate. Use the following formula to calculate the encapsulation efficiency (EE) and drug loading efficiency (DLE) of CTF in HAIR/CTF NPs:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
